OL,3,C34 barristers appointed KC in first
OL,4,Csilk call since Covid pandemic
OL,6,F34 barristers have been appointed
OL,7,FKing's Counsels in Northern Ireland in
OL,8,Fthe first silk call since the Covid
OL,9,Fpandemic.
OL,11,F12 of the newly-appointed KCs are
OL,12,Fwomen. The Bar of Northern Ireland
OL,13,Fwelcomed what it said was a three-fold
OL,14,Fincrease in female representation
OL,15,Fsince the last call in February 2020.
OL,17,FThe title of KC is awarded to
OL,18,Fbarristers deemed to have excelled in
OL,19,Fthe conduct of legal advocacy.
