OL,6,FThe advocates were appointed following
OL,7,Fa selection process at the end of last
OL,8,Fyear.
OL,10,FTheir appointment as KCs was approved
OL,11,Fby Justice Minister Naomi Long.
OL,13,FMs Long joined the new KCs at the
OL,14,FRoyal Courts of Justice in Belfast on
OL,15,FFriday as a series of ceremonies took
OL,16,Fplace to mark their achievements.
