OL,3,C34 barristers appointed KC in first
OL,4,Csilk call since Covid pandemic
OL,6,FMoira Smyth KC, chair of the Bar of
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland, welcomed the
OL,8,Fincrease in female representation,
OL,9,Fcrediting a "concerted effort" by the
OL,10,FBar Council to promote diversity at
OL,11,Fthe Bar.
OL,13,F"The new King's Counsel will serve the
OL,14,Fpublic, without fear and favour and
OL,15,Fdraw on their considerable experience
OL,16,Fof the law, advocacy and litigation to
OL,17,Frepresent the best interests of their
OL,18,Fclients and the administration of
OL,19,Fjustice," she said.
