OL,4,Csilk call since Covid pandemic
OL,6,F"They will apply their skills and
OL,7,Fexpertise in the most serious or
OL,8,Fcomplex of cases, ensuring access to
OL,9,Fjustice for all and contributing to an
OL,10,Fefficient and effective justice system.
OL,12,F"In a fast-paced, modern legal world,
OL,13,Fthe King's Counsel title is a strong
OL,14,Findication of excellence and offers a
OL,15,Freliable mark of quality.
OL,17,F"I am particularly pleased to see 12
OL,18,Fnew female KCs take silk today.
