OL,6,F"The Bar Council has made a concerted
OL,7,Feffort to promote diversity at the Bar
OL,8,Fand support our female practitioners
OL,9,Fas they serve the public interest in
OL,10,Fthe most challenging of legal matters
OL,11,Fwhilst also navigating the challenges
OL,12,Fof self-employment.
OL,14,F"Today's call to the Senior Bar is
OL,15,Fmomentous occasion for all 34 new KCs
OL,16,Fand their families.
